{"tid":1641210,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港人對呢個極權政府只會越黎越憤怒","createTime":"2019-10-09T09:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T09:20:18.000Z","uid":36134,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a019b8d350663031f92f89f1948faebd48a242e3","tid":1641210,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:19:53.000Z","msg":"成日話要對話 要和平表達意見<br />\n但另一邊縱容黑警無法無天  濫捕 <br />\n抹黑 插贓嫁禍<br />\n仲要不斷清洗異己 針對體制內既黃絲手足<br />\n同情手足既人都不能倖免<br />\n<br />\n我地每一次讓步 每一次休息<br />\n結果換黎既就係對面不斷既壓迫<br />\n不斷既清洗 不斷既打壓<br />\n瘋狂既秋後算賬 完全無停過<br />\n然後仲要問我地點解唔割蓆？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家既記住呢個政權同黑警對我地<br />\n對手足做過d咩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個仇一定要報</span></span>"},{"pid":"152942a06be6e1e65334c793f2fdb89f033444a0","tid":1641210,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:20:18.000Z","msg":"【行動核彈】隊㝝WeChat妙法！借警察報料熱線一齊將騰訊列美國制裁名單！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳情請閱：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1641145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1641145</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chrsTee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchrsTee.jpg&h=60437086&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}